WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.142
A pale hand crawls across a dark, barred window.

2
00:00:09.102 --> 00:00:13.062
A woman in white emerges from behind bars.

3
00:00:14.072 --> 00:00:25.592
The frightened man watches a woman in white, her face obscured, slowly approach him in the dark room.

4
00:00:33.475 --> 00:00:36.572
The man's face contorts in terror.

5
00:00:49.900 --> 00:00:52.925
The woman in white moves closer.

6
00:00:56.509 --> 00:01:04.000
The man looks trapped behind bars, while the woman in white watches from the shadows.

7
00:01:27.594 --> 00:01:32.800
The frightened man looks around, fear in his eyes.

8
00:01:59.042 --> 00:02:04.282
The man looks up at the smiling woman, who touches her hair.
